message.text:
Are you ready FEUture Tams from Ilocos Norte!
The FEU Admissions team is now in Ilocos Norte to help you prepare for the upcoming FEU College Admission Test (FEUCAT) for SY 2026-2027.

The FEUCAT will be held on September 20, at 8:00 AM and 1:00 PM, at the following testing center:
📍Ilocos Norte
▪️Ilocos Norte National High School (Laoag City)

Interested applicants may register at http://bit.ly/feuregistration. Walk-in applicants are also accepted on the day of the exam.
For more details, please contact our Admissions Officers provided in pubmat.
#FEUxIlocosNorte #OneFEUCAT

message.text:
Are you ready FEUture Tams from Ilocos Norte!
The FEU Admissions team is now in Ilocos Norte to help you prepare for the upcoming FEU College Admission Test (FEUCAT) for SY 2026-2027.

The FEUCAT will be held on September 20, at 8:00 AM and 1:00 PM, at the following testing center:
📍Ilocos Norte
▪️Ilocos Norte National High School (Laoag City)

Interested applicants may register at http://bit.ly/feuregistration. Walk-in applicants are also accepted on the day of the exam.
For more details, please contact our Admissions Officers provided in pubmat.
#FEUxIlocosNorte #OneFEUCAT

𝐍𝐨𝐭𝐞: Kindly check your emails for the results and confirm your application by replying to the email, and confirming your preferred interview schedule. 

Good luck with your interviews. Let us all hone and cultivate your limitless skills and potentials! 🩷

Caption by: Alexi Margarette Montecastro

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
